				<br>
				<h5><font color="white">How can I find a story I've already added to?</font></h5>
				<p><font size="2">The search bar at the top of the page allows you to search for individual stories by title.</font></p>
				<br>
				<h5><font color="white">Why can't I add to stories listed in the Story Archive?</font>3</h5>
